    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>porg -lD "tar xvf crunchbang-icon-theme.tar.gz -C /share/icons --no-same-owner" &amp;&amp;
gtk-update-icon-cache -f /share/icons/CrunchBang &amp;&amp;
gtk-update-icon-cache -f /share/icons/CrunchBang-Dark</userinput></screen>

